There are all kinds of people, insanely nice people, insanely rude people and all variations in between.  This kinda of things happens everyday in EQ and RL.  We just have to deal with the fact that some people are RUDE.<br>
<br>
We all need to remember that this topic is reserved for RANTS.  Ranting is supposed to be a way to blow off some steam and I'm sure Nef felt a little better after he posted (I know I always do).  Besides if one person reads Nef's rant and it makes them even think twice before being rude then it was worth it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
