<br>
I think this is a great site but I think I will express my opinion as much as anyone else here.  I always try to be civil and think I suceed.<br>
<br>
This tread does bring up an interesting point.<br>
<br>
There are too few spawns and areas to camp.  This is something that needs to be addressed.  I remember wandering to 3 different zones looking for a place to hunt qhwn I was level 31 (yesterday), it took almost 5 hours to find a place not camped.<br>
<br>
This is a serious problem and it will eventually degrade the player comunity into a screaming, yelling, petitioning bunch of apes.  I hope VI adds more spawns or splits more servers.<br>
<br>
You have to admit it could only help.<br>
<br>
